l.<br>
<br>
<br>
You get this quest from  Romar Sunto in the Temple of Solusek Ro. He will give you a bag in which you collect 10 coins in different cities around the world. He will sell you a book on where to find all 10 coins for 50gp.  The coins are called an old silver coin, and can be found in the following places: <br>
<br>
1. Ak'anon - Near great wheel (not in water); <br>
2. Kaladim - Pool by warrior's guild; <br>
3. Erudin - in the pool outside the guilds in the palace; <br>
4. Qeynos - Under Temple of Life UFO in the Koalindl Fish Pool; <br>
5. Halas - In lake in front of city to the left of docks on a ledge; <br>
6. Oggok - in lake near warrior guild at the north end; <br>
7. Grobb - in pool near bar where you first enter the zone; <br>
8. Neriak - Ouside blind fish window near ice comet rod; <br>
9. Felwithe - at the edge of the fishing pond; and <br>
10. Freeport - Under the mage guild building in the water. <br>
<br>
Take the 10 coins and combine them in the coin pouch to get a &quot;Coin Of Tash&quot; and a coin pouch.<br>
<br>
Next, Take the coin to Tarn Visilin in the Highkeep Library and give him the coin. He will enchant it into a glowing coin of tash and give it back. Increases Beta Neutral faction.<br>
<br>
Then take the coin to Mizr N'Mar in Neriak Library and give him the coin. He enchants it into a gleaming coin of tash. <br>
<br>
Then take the coin to Raine Beteria in Erudin Library and give her the coin. It is important to note that you must have a high faction with her or she will just keep the coin and give you nothing in return. Casting Illusion Erudite and Benevolence before giving her the coin should take care of this problem. Increases Erudin factions.<br>
<br>
Take the coin that she gives you and return it to Romar and receive the tashania scroll (level 44 enchanter spell), which is no drop, so if you want this spell you have to do this quest.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub24.ezboard.com/ukelila.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kelila</A> at: 11/9/00 2:36:35 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub24.ezboard.com/fhallofillusionsfrm1.showMessage?topicID=7.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub24.ezboard.com/fhallofillusionsfrm1.showMessage?topicID=18.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub24.ezboard.com/fhallofillusionsfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=3.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub24.ezboard.com/fhallofillusionsfrm1.threadControl?topicID=3.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub24.ezboard.com/fhallofillusionsfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub24.ezboard.com/fhallofillusionsfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub24.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="hallofillusionsfrm3">Spells<option value="hallofillusionsfrm2">Research<option value="hallofillusionsfrm1">Quests<option value="hallofillusionsfrm4">Jewel Craft<option value="hallofillusio